# SDLC Skills — Product Owner

## Your Skills (12)

### Feature Evaluation
- `/feature-balance-sheet quick '<idea>'` — Quick go/no-go cost-benefit filter before writing a spec
- `/feature-balance-sheet deep specs/NNN/spec.md` — Full portfolio analysis after spec is written
- `/spec-gen '<feature request>'` — Generate a structured specification from a feature idea
- `/decision-log capture specs/NNN/spec.md` — Record decision rationale alongside spec creation

### Quality & Compliance
- `/quality-gate spec-to-plan specs/NNN/spec.md` — Validate spec meets quality bar before planning
- `/gate-briefing specs/NNN/ --audience executive` — Generate decision briefing for approval gates
- `/drift-detector scan --all` — Detect spec-to-implementation divergence

### Sprint & Scope
- `/scope-tracker report specs/NNN/` — Track scope changes with effort deltas
- `/board-sync push specs/NNN/tasks.md` — Push work items to PM tool (Jira, Azure Boards, etc.)
- `/report-trends dashboard` — Health dashboard with trend analysis
- `/risk-tracker scan --all` — Living risk register with auto-escalation

### Release
- `/release-readiness-checker vX.Y.Z` — Pre-release go/no-go verdict
- `/release-notes --version vX.Y.Z` — Auto-generate categorized release notes

## Your Pipelines (3)

### Feature Intake
Evaluate a feature request end-to-end:
```
/run-pipeline product-owner/feature-intake 'Add SSO login'
```
Chain: balance-sheet (quick) → spec-gen → quality-gate → balance-sheet (deep) → gate-briefing

### Sprint Health
Sprint dashboard with scope and risk tracking:
```
/run-pipeline product-owner/sprint-health
```
Chain: scope-tracker → board-sync → report-trends → risk-tracker

### Release Signoff
Release go/no-go decision:
```
/run-pipeline product-owner/release-signoff vX.Y.Z
```
Chain: release-readiness-checker → gate-briefing → release-notes
